00:05:29.290 --> 00:05:29.720
Tamam!

00:05:37.210 --> 00:05:37.800
Akagi-kun!

00:05:37.800 --> 00:05:38.390
İyi misin?

00:05:38.870 --> 00:05:40.300
Güzel pas!

00:05:42.900 --> 00:05:44.320
Sert adam!

