00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:02.320
Akagi-kun!

00:07:02.500 --> 00:07:03.070
Ama...

00:07:04.380 --> 00:07:05.760
Mitsui'yi ben savunacağım!

00:07:06.270 --> 00:07:07.180
İlginç!

00:07:07.530 --> 00:07:09.940
Durdurabilirsen durdur, goril!

00:07:10.190 --> 00:07:10.970
Seni durduracağım!

00:07:11.420 --> 00:07:12.480
Bana goril deme!

00:07:13.080 --> 00:07:15.870
